M|rules|title: Parallel Data Fetching with Component Composition
M|rules|impact: CRITICAL
M|rules|impactDescription: eliminates server-side waterfalls
M|rules|tags: server, rsc, parallel-fetching, composition
M|rules|React Server Components execute sequentially within a tree. Restructure with composition to parallelize data fetching.
M|rules|**Incorrect (Sidebar waits for Page's fetch to complete):**
M|rules|```tsx
M|rules|export default async function Page() {
M|rules|const header = await fetchHeader()
M|rules|return (
M|rules|<div>
M|rules|<div>{header}</div>
M|rules|<Sidebar />
M|rules|</div>
M|rules|)
M|rules|}
M|rules|async function Sidebar() {
M|rules|const items = await fetchSidebarItems()
M|rules|return <nav>{items.map(renderItem)}</nav>
M|rules|}
M|rules|```
M|rules|**Correct (both fetch simultaneously):**
M|rules|```tsx
M|rules|async function Header() {
M|rules|const data = await fetchHeader()
M|rules|return <div>{data}</div>
M|rules|}
M|rules|async function Sidebar() {
M|rules|const items = await fetchSidebarItems()
M|rules|return <nav>{items.map(renderItem)}</nav>
M|rules|}
M|rules|export default function Page() {
M|rules|return (
M|rules|<div>
M|rules|<Header />
M|rules|<Sidebar />
M|rules|</div>
M|rules|)
M|rules|}
M|rules|```
M|rules|**Alternative with children prop:**
M|rules|```tsx
M|rules|async function Header() {
M|rules|const data = await fetchHeader()
M|rules|return <div>{data}</div>
M|rules|}
M|rules|async function Sidebar() {
M|rules|const items = await fetchSidebarItems()
M|rules|return <nav>{items.map(renderItem)}</nav>
M|rules|}
M|rules|function Layout({ children }: { children: ReactNode }) {
M|rules|return (
M|rules|<div>
M|rules|<Header />
M|rules|{children}
M|rules|</div>
M|rules|)
M|rules|}
M|rules|export default function Page() {
M|rules|return (
M|rules|<Layout>
M|rules|<Sidebar />
M|rules|</Layout>
M|rules|)
M|rules|}
M|rules|```